  "prompt": "Which are the top ninja dragon games?",
  "response": "As of my last data update in October 2023, the concept of \"ninja dragon games\" typically involves action-packed games featuring ninja and sometimes dragon elements. While there may not be a specific genre universally recognized as \"ninja dragon games,\" there are several popular games that involve ninjas, dragons, or both. Here are some notable games you may find interesting:\n\n1. **Nioh Series**: An action RPG that combines ninja elements with samurai lore, featuring challenging gameplay and mythical creatures.\n\n2. **Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice**: A game that features a shinobi protagonist and has intense combat, though it primarily focuses on the ninja aspect rather than dragons.\n\n3. **Ninja Gaiden Series**: A classic series focusing on ninja protagonist Ryu Hayabusa, known for its fast-paced and challenging gameplay.\n\n4. **The Messenger**: A side-scrolling action game that starts off as a platformer and evolves into a metroidvania, with a ninja protagonist facing various mythical creatures.\n\n5. **Dragon\u2019s Dogma**: Although not specifically a ninja game, this fantasy RPG includes dragons and has intense combat where you can create characters with ninja-like abilities.\n\n6. **Tenchu Series**: Focuses on stealth and ninja combat, though it occasionally includes mythical elements.\n\nThese games may not fit the exact \"ninja dragon\" theme, but they provide exciting gameplay elements related to ninjas and/or dragons. Be sure to check the latest releases and reviews for any new games that might fit your interests better.",
